ZH: 我爱我的家人。
EN: I love my family.

ZH: 他们深深地相爱着。
EN: They are deeply in love with each other.

ZH: 她以爱心照顾弱者。
EN: She takes care of the weak with love.

ZH: 我爱读书。
EN: I love reading.

ZH: 你最爱的食物是什么？
EN: What is your favorite food?

ZH: 她热爱大自然。
EN: She has a deep love for nature.

ZH: 孩子们都爱看动画片。
EN: Kids all love watching cartoons.

ZH: 这只小狗非常受宠爱。
EN: This little dog is very loved.

ZH: 他以爱心和善行闻名。
EN: He is famous for his love and kindness.

ZH: 我爱逛街购物。
EN: I love going shopping.

ZH: 爱是世界的语言。
EN: Love is the language of the world.

ZH: 他的爱使我感到温暖。
EN: His love makes me feel warm.

ZH: 她对你充满了爱意。
EN: She is full of love for you.

ZH: 爱让人变得勇敢。
EN: Love makes people brave.

ZH: 你能感受到父母的爱吗？
EN: Can you feel your parents' love?

ZH: 他们在爱河中失去了方向感。
EN: They lost their sense of direction in the river of love.

ZH: 爱是无私的。
EN: Love is selfless.

ZH: 她爱着他，尽管他并不完美。
EN: She loves him, despite his imperfections.

ZH: 他用深情款款的方式表达着对她的爱。
EN: He expresses his love for her in a tender way.

ZH: 爱和关心是我们生活中最重要的。
EN: Love and care are the most important things in our lives.
